Game class
----------

This event operates on an instance of the [game class](Game_class "Game class") type {{{gameclass}}}

Description
-----------

Disables the ability of the weapon to fire.

Usage
-----

*void* weaponOutOfAmmo()

Parameters
----------

This event does not accept parameters.

